<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.5.3">
  <compounddef id="isbnapi" kind="page">
    <compoundname>isbnapi</compoundname>
    <title>ISBNdb API</title>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>You <bold>must</bold> create an API Key at <ulink url="https://isbndb.com/account/dev/keys/generate.html">https://isbndb.com/account/dev/keys/generate.html</ulink> before you can use this function.</para></simplesect>
All calls to the API return data in an <ref refid="classXML" kindref="compound">XML</ref> format. A request of <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>http:</highlight><highlight class="comment">//isbndb.com/api/books.xml?access_key=12345678&amp;index1=isbn&amp;value1=0596002068</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> would return the following: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>&lt;?xml<sp/>version=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;1.0&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>encoding=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">?&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>&lt;ISBNdb<sp/>server_time=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;2005-02-25T23:03:41&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>&lt;BookList<sp/>total_results=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>page_size=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;10&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>page_number=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>shown_results=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;BookData<sp/>book_id=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;somebook&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>isbn=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;0123456789&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;Title&gt;Interesting<sp/>Book&lt;/Title&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;TitleLong&gt;Interesting<sp/>Book:<sp/>Read<sp/>it<sp/>or<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">else</highlight><highlight class="normal">..&lt;/TitleLong&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;AuthorsText&gt;John<sp/>Doe&lt;/AuthorsText&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;PublisherText&gt;Acme<sp/>Publishing&lt;/PublisherText&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;/BookData&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>&lt;/BookList&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>&lt;/ISBNdb&gt;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> <simplesect kind="see"><para><ulink url="https://isbndb.com/docs/api/">https://isbndb.com/docs/api/</ulink> </para><para><ulink url="https://isbndb.com/">https://isbndb.com/</ulink> </para></simplesect>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
  </compounddef>
